---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import ProseSection from '../components/ProseSection.astro';
import CtaButton from '../components/CtaButton.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Our Environment"
  description="A safe, calm and joyful learning environment in Srinagar, thoughtfully designed to feel like a home away from home for children aged 2–3."
>
  <PageHero eyebrow="A home away from home" title="Our Environment" accent="green">
    <p>Step inside and you may never want to leave, and neither will your little one.</p>
  </PageHero>

  <section class="section container">
    <ProseSection
      image="/images/environment/environment.webp"
      alt="A child playing on the alphabet rug in our bright playroom"
      accent="green"
    >
      <p class="lead">
        Toddler World is a place that draws children in. Once they walk through the door, they
        simply don't want to leave. Our thoughtfully designed environment supports every child's
        growth, while giving families the reassurance of genuine, high-quality care.
      </p>

      <h2>Peace of mind</h2>
      <p>
        We know the safety and well-being of your child is your top priority, and it's ours too. We go
        above and beyond to make sure every child feels safe, comfortable and cared for, across
        every part of our programme.
      </p>

      <h2>Home away from home</h2>
      <p>
        We give your child a true home away from home. That warm, personal feeling carries through
        everything, from our people to our buildings and grounds, which are designed to be fun,
        interactive and full of life. Here, your child takes their very first steps toward a
        lifelong love of learning.
      </p>

      <h2>A caring growth environment</h2>
      <p>Our dedicated, trained staff shape a space that gently caters to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>The different stages of a child's development</li>
        <li>The individual differences between children</li>
        <li>The varied skills and potential of each little one</li>
        <li>And, just as importantly, every kind of intelligence</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Every corner is designed to give your child the best possible experience.</p>

      <div class="btn-row">
        <CtaButton href="/play-equipment">Explore our facilities</CtaButton>
        <CtaButton variant="ghost" href="/welcome">Come and visit</CtaButton>
      </div>
    </ProseSection>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .btn-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--sp-3);
    margin-top: var(--sp-6);
  }
</style>
